title: Silver 3 but going against low golds?

replies.body: Im high silver going against mid plats. Please dont complain.
Happens a lot. Nothing unusual tbh.
Wow I just went against a whole team of gold with my team who is full of silver 3 -  1.
Gold 5 doesn't mean they are low golds, they are likely mid Silver in MMR, but still in gold due to the inability to fall out of gold (because you have to get down to silver 5 MMR to fall)
